title: Doobie Brothers - Rockin Down The Higway - DVD - cOOt
description:
It seems that everywhere I looked I was unable to find this torrent anywhere, with the exception of some dead ones. So it is my pleasure to bring to you this rip of my favorite Doobie Brothers concert. I must apologize in advance for a slight skip in track twelve, as is my copy has been around for awhile, but it in no way ruins the show.
